{"tid":2374122,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新貓入屋一星期最鐘意半夜賴尿落床","createTime":"2021-01-21T04:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T12:08:37.000Z","uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2223f88ee1133417591e809005ff3c5b1a868d42","tid":2374122,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T04:05:55.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身養緊一隻舊貓8個月大<br />\n因為新舊貓要隔離，所以將新貓困係我間房<br />\n每晚都有放風俾舊貓同佢玩下<br />\n唔知係咪佢唔鐘意舊貓，定舊貓玩得太大力<br />\n玩玩下fee舊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入返房就係床單、被上面搵位柯尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝6點又feel到張床又熱又濕，我就知道佢又賴尿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一日又試過冇放風，但都照係床柯<br />\n連續幾晚都係咁<br />\n係佢冇安全感定貪得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就嚟崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdddd1d7d8cba0e092622d1b8300a6b8f4d2f17d","tid":2374122,"uid":126903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2223f88ee1133417591e809005ff3c5b1a868d42","tid":2374122,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T04:05:55.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身養緊一隻舊貓8個月大<br />\n因為新舊貓要隔離，所以將新貓困係我間房<br />\n每晚都有放風俾舊貓同佢玩下<br />\n唔知係咪佢唔鐘意舊貓，定舊貓玩得太大力<br />\n玩玩下fee舊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入返房就係床單、被上面搵位柯尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝6點又feel到張床又熱又濕，我就知道佢又賴尿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一日又試過冇放風，但都照係床柯<br />\n連續幾晚都係咁<br />\n係佢冇安全感定貪得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 